<mxCell id="c24" value="Lifecycle legend (marker text is the primary meaning; border style supports it):&lt;br&gt;Target: solid blue border, light blue fill.&lt;br&gt;Mixed: solid amber border, light amber fill.&lt;br&gt;Transitional: dashed purple border, light purple fill.&lt;br&gt;Legacy retained initially: thick black border, grey fill." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#666666;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="660" width="560" height="150" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
<mxCell id="c25" value="Limitation: this is a mixed-state landscape. It does not imply that every target system exists fully today. Relationship labels are high level. Detailed interface mechanisms (APIs, events, files, adapters) belong in an integration view or interface catalogue, not in this landscape map." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF8DC;strokeColor=#8A6D3B;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="610" y="660" width="570" height="150" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
